column5: WOW is an understatement. Thx for posting.

Thats unreal..Fresh water fishing would never be the same again..lol awesome  They do travel to freshwater and in Canada too, they have been found in the Saguenay River in Quebec if you want to give them a go. Just saw a show on National Geographic about them there a few weeks ago.
